data.description: Great location in an amenity-rich neighborhood in Rock Hill! Open Concept with casual living spaces. Large Great room open to kitchen with breakfast area. Bedrooms upstairs with walk-in closets. Freshly painted interior and clean exterior with great curb appeal. New microwave and oven were installed in 2023. Close to schools, hospital, shopping, dining, & easy, convenient access to I-77. Come see this charming move-in ready home!
